# ─── Database (Supabase PostgreSQL) ─────────────────────────────────────────
# Get these from: supabase.com → project → Settings → Database → Connection string
# Use "Transaction" mode URL for DATABASE_URL (pooled)
# Use "Session" mode URL for DIRECT_URL (direct)
